#### 1. Layout Basics
---
##### 수업 소스
```erb
<App>
<!--  <StackPanel Orientation="Vertical" Padding="10" Margin="10">
	<Text Alignment="Center" Margin="10">some text</Text> 
	<Button Text="the button"/>
	<Slider />
	<Switch />
 </StackPanel> -->

<DockPanel Padding="10">
	<Text Dock="Right">some text</Text> 
	<Button Margin="10" Text="the button" Dock="Top"/>
	<Slider />
	<Switch />
</DockPanel>
</App>

```
